description: Team Red leads the board with 492 points to Blue's 377. It's still a close match and is anyone's game at this point. Since the Rookies both started out on the mats in round 1, the veterans start out in round 2. But the Clash between the two titans doesn't last long as they use their tags to get out of troublesome situations. The Rookies are picking up moves quickly and giving the vets a run for their money.
title: Round 2 Tag Team Bella Rossi, Mischa Brookes vs. Darling, Rilynn Rae
